y":"RK Bagatsing (born Ramon Khino San Diego Bagatsing on 09 May 1988) is a Filipino actor. He is best known for his roles in the films Apocalypse Child (2015), Cuddle Weather (2019), Uninvited (2024), and Love Child (2025), among others.","name":"RK Bagatsing","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PH","iso_639_1":"tl","name":"","english_name":"Tagalog","data":{"biography":"","name":"RK Bagatsing","primary":true}}]}},"person_78019_translations":{"at":1772689465480,"data":{"id":78019,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"IT","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano","english_name":"Italian","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Peter Polycarpou","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"彼得·多卡普","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"彼得·多卡普","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Питер Поликарпу","primary":false}}]}},"person_112982_translations":{"at":1772689465895,"data":{"id":112982,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Pinky Cheung Man-Chi grew up in Hong Kong, but spent some of her schooling years abroad in the USA and Japan. After the attention brought by her presence in the Miss Asia contest, she was signed up by ATV and was in a number of TV series – one of the most popular being My Date with a Vampire. After this she embarked on a series of horror films.","name":"Pinky Cheung Man-Chi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"张文慈，香港电影及电视剧演员，曾参加亚洲小姐竞选，取得最完美体态大奖，后加入亚洲电视，并曾参与演出多部电视剧集。现已结束与亚视合约，为自由女艺员，以性感著称。","name":"张文慈","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"張文慈，香港女演員，曾是亞洲電視旗下藝人，現為無綫電視基本藝人合約及前邵氏兄弟藝員。\n\n1996 年，張文慈參加亞洲小姐競選，於準決賽取得「最完美體態葆露絲大獎」，並順利晉身決賽。雖然決賽晉身前八名，但是最後三甲不入。之後簽約亞洲電視，並曾參與演出多部電視劇，較著名的有《肥貓正傳》、《縱橫四海》、《我和殭屍有個約會》系列。其後又被文雋發掘，與影王朝公司簽約拍攝多部電影，首部電影是《97 古惑仔之戰無不勝》，其他電影包括《火爆刑警》、《俠骨仁心》、《新紮師姐》及《黑白森林》等。除拍攝電影外，亦在亞洲電視參與演出劇集及綜藝節目等工作，並參與登台及演出香港電台電視節目。\n\n2010 年 3 月，張文慈離開亞洲電視。2012 年於亞洲電視五十五週年獲頒「ATV55 年女藝人獎」。2013 年，她轉向電影界發展，2016 年 9 月於活動中表示已簽約無綫電視兩年，主要參與劇集拍攝。2018 年在《宮心計 2 深宮計》飾演司膳汪敏，演技大獲好評，同年又於台慶劇《跳躍生命線》飾演麥愛花，與馬德鐘飾演的麥在田為姊弟，而當中一幕是被其痛罵時強忍淚水，收放自如的演技再獲觀眾及網民大讚。","name":"張文慈","primary":true}}]}},"person_5983851_translations":{"at":1772689468623,"data":{"id":5983851,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"SE","iso_639_1":"sv","name":"svenska","english_name":"Swedish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Al Michaels","primary":true}}]}},"person_5983853_translations":{"at":1772689469031,"data":{"id":5983853,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"SE","iso_639_1":"sv","name":"svenska","english_name":"Swedish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ralph Cox","primary":true}}]}},"person_3177579_translations":{"at":1772689477004,"data":{"id":3177579,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"height: 164.0cm\n\nMBTI: ENFJ\n\nHOBBY: Watching movies / Cooking","name":"Vivi Chen","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"陳昕葳","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"陈昕葳","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"陳昕葳","primary":false}}]}}}}